islike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:10:43.000Z","msg":"RTHK:<br />\n理大再有兩名留守者在義務急救員陪同下離開校園<br />\n<br />\n零晨時份，理大再有兩名留守者在義務急救員陪同下離開校園，他們先被帶到向警方登記，再送往醫院檢查，暫時未有被捕。據悉，2人分別是21和22歲，都是香港城市大學學生。游說他們離開的急救員表示，這兩名留守者狀態十分惡劣、身心俱疲，有創傷後遺症徵狀，留守期間一直擔心警察有下一步行動，花了很多時間才說服兩人離開。該名急救員又說，估計理大校園至少還有20人，部分更出現輕生念頭，據他了解曾有至少5人鎅手自殘，情況令人憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n2019-11-25 03:56:31"},{"pid":"24efc274bbfde582fb8102ba88310e44f80d19fc","tid":1752284,"uid":81725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:11:06.000Z","msg":"poly手足們，香港人沒有忘記到你地"},{"pid":"34356f6c63b388f94683e0ef32eb785023f1e0e0","tid":1752284,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c594ec784ba62fbdf3c1da326cc5cd2bf1d6d98","tid":1752284,"uid":32906,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:43:04.000Z","msg":"到最後都無偷走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佩服"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本偷走到就應該偷走"},{"pid":"7d53ef4c856b2e97287d9b60b170ba265548651d","tid":1752284,"uid":252740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:11:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146500e4f6d82c7e8c23fb601600bd04d6f72dcd","tid":1752284,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:11:53.000Z","msg":"出返黎一齊繼續抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />辛苦手足"},{"pid":"8b1223c4a3e8fea23e4fe5c936f5bacf24e49087","tid":1752284,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2491324009771fc2c4a9a19822e709e0e03df83","tid":1752284,"uid":185854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r